      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On note $\\omega = e^{2i\\pi/n}$, $\\alpha = e^{i\\pi/n}$ et $D$ le déterminant\n$n \\times n$ : $D = \\det\\Bigl( \\omega^{(k-1)(l-1)} \\Bigr)$.",
        "html": "<p>On note <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\omega = e^{2i\\pi/n}\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha = e^{i\\pi/n}\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D\\)</span> le déterminant <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n \\times n\\)</span> : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D = \\det\\Bigl( \\omega^{(k-1)(l-1)} \\Bigr)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4fad0a9b-6982-4bcb-b7ee-0e2aa164d90d",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $D^2$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "539e2732-8e38-4825-8f1c-e16031fd0253",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $D = \\prod_{k < \\ell}(\\omega^\\ell - \\omega^k)\n            = \\prod_{k < \\ell}\\left(\\alpha^{k+\\ell}\\cdot\n              2i\\sin\\frac {\\ell-k}n \\pi\\right)$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D = \\prod_{k &lt; \\ell}(\\omega^\\ell - \\omega^k)\n            = \\prod_{k &lt; \\ell}\\left(\\alpha^{k+\\ell}\\cdot\n              2i\\sin\\frac {\\ell-k}n \\pi\\right)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "533e471f-535a-4f0a-89a7-650a1884b107",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Exprimer $D$ sous forme trigonométrique.",
        "html": "<p>Exprimer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D\\)</span> sous forme trigonométrique.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d41acb74-d444-48f4-854f-fd1292e39ae7",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$M^2 = \\begin{pmatrix}n      &0      &\\dots     &0     \\cr\n                              0      &0      &          &n     \\cr\n                              \\vdots &       &\\dots           \\cr\n                              0      &n      &          &0     \\cr \\end{pmatrix}\n                \\Rightarrow  D^2 = \\varepsilon_{n-1}n^n$.\n$n^{n/2}\\exp\\left({i\\frac \\pi4 (n-1)(3n+2)}\\right)$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(M^2 = \\begin{pmatrix}n      &amp;0      &amp;\\dots     &amp;0     \\cr\n                              0      &amp;0      &amp;          &amp;n     \\cr\n                              \\vdots &amp;       &amp;\\dots           \\cr\n                              0      &amp;n      &amp;          &amp;0     \\cr \\end{pmatrix}\n                \\Rightarrow  D^2 = \\varepsilon_{n-1}n^n\\)</span>. <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n^{n/2}\\exp\\left({i\\frac \\pi4 (n-1)(3n+2)}\\right)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
